Authentication and Autherization

user ko profile dene se pehle check karna hota hai ke user hai kaun



cookies and session:
server har baar bhul jata hai ki aap  kaun ho toh har baar wo appse puchega ki aap kaun ho 

server browser ko cookie(unkown string) send kardega 

fir wo cookie har request ke sath jata hai jisse userid-pass nhi dena padta server cookie se hi verify kar dega


sabse pehle humein kuch cheejein seekhni hai alag alag 


1) cookie kaise set kardega
ii) bcryt kaise use karte hai for password encryption and decryption
iii)jwt kya hai and jwt main data kaise store karein and baahar  nikalein



